Halve @Ciabatta Bread{2%unit}; toast until golden brown in a #toaster{}.

Wash and dry produce.

Quarter @Lemon{1}. Roughly chop @Dill{1/4%ounce} fronds. Trim and thinly slice
@Mini Cucumber{1} into rounds. Halve, core, and thinly slice @Apple{1}.

In a #medium bowl{}, toss together @Arugula{2%ounce}, a drizzle of @Olive Oil{1%tsp}, juice
from one lemon wedge (juice from two wedges for 4 servings), @Salt{pinch},
@Pepper{pinch}, and as much dill as you like.

Spread bottom halves of ciabattas with @Cream Cheese{4%tbsp} and @Red Pepper Jam{1}. Top 
with cucumber slices and as much arugula salad as you like. Close sandwiches.

Halve sandwiches on a diagonal and divide between plates. Serve apple
slices and any remaining arugula salad on the side.